# readLines("sample_new.dat", n = 10)
ingest_vector <- readLines("../sample_new.dat", n=2)
header_vector <- str_split(ingest_vector[2], pattern = '\",\"')

for (value in header_vector) {
  column_vector <- value
  print(value)
}

—- Clean and Pivot —-

ingest_tibble <- ingest_tibble %>% 
  rename(TIMESTAMP = X.TIMESTAMP, BattVolt = Batt_volt) %>%
  rename_with(~gsub(".", "", .x, fixed = TRUE)) %>% 
  pivot_longer (
    cols = -c(TIMESTAMP, RECORD, BattVolt, PTemp), 
    names_to = c(".value", "Probe"), 
    names_sep = -1
  ) %>% 
  mutate(across(TIMESTAMP, as.POSIXct))

# rename columns by stripping last _ 
cleaning_column_names <- colnames(ingest_tibble)
cleaned <- stri_replace_last(cleaning_column_names, regex="_", replacement="")
colnames(ingest_tibble) <- cleaned

—- Mutating and Math —-

manipulation_tibble <- ingest_tibble %>% 
  # OUTER
  mutate(Vh_HRM_Outer = (2*k*Alpha_Outer)/(x_d_outer + x_u_outer) + (x_d_outer - x_u_outer)/(2*(t - (t_0/2)))) %>% 
  mutate(Vh_Tmax_Outer = sqrt( ((4*k)/t_0) * log(1 - (t_0/Tmax_Outer)) + (x_d_outer ^ 2)/(Tmax_Outer * (Tmax_Outer - t_0)) )) %>% 
  
  # INNER
  mutate(Vh_HRM_Inner = (2*k*Alpha_Inner)/(x_d_inner + x_d_inner) + (x_d_inner - x_u_inner)/(2*(t - (t_0/2)))) %>% 
  mutate(Vh_Tmax_Inner = sqrt( ((4*k)/t_0) * log(1 - (t_0/Tmax_Inner)) + (x_d_inner ^ 2)/(Tmax_Inner * (Tmax_Inner - t_0))) )
## Warning in sqrt(((4 * k)/t_0) * log(1 - (t_0/Tmax_Outer)) + (x_d_outer^2)/
## (Tmax_Outer * : NaNs produced
## Warning in sqrt(((4 * k)/t_0) * log(1 - (t_0/Tmax_Inner)) + (x_d_inner^2)/
## (Tmax_Inner * : NaNs produced

# Filtering for Vh_Corr
filtering_tibble <- filtering_tibble %>% 
  mutate(Vh_Corr_Inner = case_when(
    Beta_Inner <= 1 ~ Vh_HRM_Inner, 
    Beta_Inner > 1 ~ Vh_Tmax_Inner)
  ) %>% 
  mutate(Vh_Corr_Outer = case_when(
    Beta_Outer <= 1 ~ Vh_HRM_Outer, 
    Beta_Outer > 1 ~ Vh_Tmax_Outer)
  )
